// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-2972 — Mass File Rename (handala)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: ef47da83-55b7-5ca4-81c8-206345dacfee

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
